V0304_01_00_00_0.text: You're about ta learn that I upgraded my Duelin' big time!

V0304_01_00_01_0.text: I put my whole heart into dis deck!

V0304_01_00_02_0.text: If I believe in my cards, they won't let me down!

V0304_01_00_03_0.text: I'll take on everyone, from da tough to da super tough!

V0304_01_00_03_1.text: Dat's da only way I can become a true Duelist!

V0304_01_00_04_0.text:
Yugi! 
Let's let our cards do da talkin'!

V0304_01_00_05_0.text:
Kaiba!
If you wanna Duel Yugi, you gotta get thru me first!

V0304_01_00_06_0.text: Ya look grown up, but I bet you're still a kid on da inside!

V0304_01_00_07_0.text: My dream's to be a professional Duelist!

V0304_01_00_07_1.text: And I'll make my dream a reality!

V0304_01_00_08_0.text: Have ya ranked up from a newb to a newbie yet, Tristan?

V0304_01_00_09_0.text:
Aigami...?
...Oh yeah. Dat's your name.
Aigami...

V0304_01_00_11_0.text:
Scud!
Your bullyin' days are over!

V0304_03_00_05_0.text: Dis may look bad, but I'm just warmin' up!

V0304_08_00_00_0.text: I can always count on my sheep!

V0304_08_00_01_1.text: It returns all Spell and Traps on da field to our hands!

V0304_08_00_02_0.text:
I activate my Quick-Play Spell!
Graceful Dice!

V0304_08_00_03_0.text:
Dis card swaps attack and defense points!
Shield & Sword!

V0304_08_00_04_0.text:
Here goes!
Da Spell Card, Polymerization!

V0304_08_00_05_0.text: I gotta take a gamble, but dat ain't nuthin' new for me!

V0304_08_00_06_0.text: I got a Question for ya!

V0304_08_00_06_1.text: What's da monster at da bottom of my Graveyard?

V0304_08_00_07_0.text: I'll use dis to send a monster to da Graveyard!

V0304_08_00_09_0.text: Dis is da perfect field for my monsters!

V0304_08_00_10_0.text:
I activate my Equip Spell!
Power 'em up, Salamandra!

V0304_08_00_12_0.text:
Electricity zaps when it's in water!
Lightning Blade!

V0304_08_00_13_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
Red-Eyes Insight!

V0304_08_00_14_0.text: I'm gonna Fusion Summon Red-Eyes with this!

V0304_08_00_14_1.text: I activate da Spell Card, Red-Eyes Fusion!

V0304_08_00_15_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
Cards of the Red Stone!

V0304_08_00_16_1.text: I activate my Trap Card, Trap Hole!

V0304_08_00_18_0.text: Can ya find which hole da monster's hidin' in?

V0304_08_00_19_0.text: I'm stealin' your Spell Card from your Graveyard!

V0304_08_00_21_1.text: I use my Trap Card, Magical Arm Shield!

V0304_08_00_22_0.text: Here's my Trap Card, Kunai with Chain!

V0304_08_00_23_0.text:
I activate my Trap Card!
Metalmorph!

V0304_08_00_24_0.text:
I activate my Trap Card!
Red-Eyes Fang with Chain!

V0304_08_00_25_0.text: I'll use Red-Eyes Fang with Chain's other effect!

V0304_08_00_26_0.text:
I'm usin' Red-Eyes Spirit!
Come on back, Red-Eyes!

V0304_08_00_27_0.text:
Red-Eyes ain't going down for nuthin'!
Red-Eyes Burn!

V0304_08_00_28_0.text:
I activate my Continuous Trap!
Return of the Red-Eyes!

V0304_08_00_29_0.text: Return of the Red-Eyes calls back a Normal Monster!

V0304_08_00_30_0.text: By destroying Return of the Red-Eyes, I resummon Red-Eyes!

V0304_09_00_00_0.text: I believe in ya, Time Wizard!

V0304_40_00_00_0.text:
Oh yeah!
All your monsters are destroyed!

V0304_09_00_05_0.text: Rocket Warrior cuts your monster's ATK down!

V0304_09_00_06_0.text: Gearfried's armor won't let him don any Equip Spells!

V0304_09_00_07_0.text: Gearfried can shed an Equip Card to destroy a Spell or Trap!

V0304_09_00_08_0.text: Gearfried's other effect swaps an Equip Card for Red-Eyes!

V0304_09_00_09_0.text: When Gilford is summoned, it destroys all your monsters!

V0304_09_00_10_0.text: I activate Red-Eyes Retro Dragon's effect from my hand!

V0304_09_00_10_1.text: I turn back time to resurrect Red-Eyes!

V0304_09_00_11_1.text: I can summon a bonus Red-Eyes this turn!

V0304_09_00_12_0.text: I equip Red-Eyes Baby Dragon on Red-Eyes to revive it!

V0304_09_00_13_0.text: Da equipped Red-Eyes Baby Dragon's effect activates!

V0304_09_00_13_1.text: I add a card to my hand!

V0304_09_00_14_0.text: I use Red-Eyes Wyvern's effect to Special Summon Red-Eyes!

V0304_09_00_15_0.text: I send Black Dragon's Chick to the Grave to summon Red-Eyes!

V0304_09_00_16_0.text: I Tribute The Black Stone of Legend!

V0304_09_00_16_1.text: Dat lets me call out Red-Eyes from my deck!

V0304_09_00_17_0.text: The Black Stone of Legend activates from my Graveyard!

V0304_09_00_18_0.text: I equip Black Metal Dragon on Red-Eyes!

V0304_09_00_19_0.text: Black Metal Dragon's effect adds a card to my hand!

V0304_09_00_21_0.text: Dat won't work against Red-Eyes Slash Dragon!

V0304_09_00_22_0.text: Red-Eyes Slash Dragon may go down, but I still got dis!

V0304_09_00_23_0.text:
It ain't over!
Take Red-Eyes Black Flare Dragon's effect!

V0304_09_00_24_0.text: Red-Eyes Alternative Black Dragon resurrects my Red-Eyes!

V0304_09_00_25_0.text: Red-Eyes Archfiend of Lightning! Light 'em up!

V0304_09_00_26_0.text: Meteor Black Comet Dragon's effect activates!

V0304_09_00_27_0.text: Meteor Black Comet Dragon's effect activates!

V0304_09_00_27_1.text: It revives a Normal Monster from da Graveyard!

V0304_09_00_28_0.text: Archfiend Black Skull Dragon's effect activates!

V0304_09_00_28_1.text: Red-Eyes may be in my Grave, but it can still burn you up!

V0304_10_00_03_0.text: Dis is da one I want!

V0304_11_01_00_0.text: I Summon my monster in Defense Position!

V0304_37_00_00_0.text: After a thousand years, Baby Dragon grows up!

V0304_13_00_09_0.text:
I'm playin' dis card!
Giltia the D. Knight!

V0304_13_00_10_0.text: Mako trusted me to use dis card right, so I'm gonna!

V0304_13_00_15_0.text: Espa Roba gave me dis card!

V0304_13_00_18_0.text:
Dis guy's bringin' the thunder!
Gilford the Lightning!

V0304_13_00_19_0.text: We're gonna fight together 'til we're champions!

V0304_13_00_22_0.text: I Special Summon Red-Eyes Black Metal Dragon!

V0304_13_00_30_0.text: Joinin' me is Red-Eyes Slash Dragon!

V0304_13_00_32_0.text: Let's go, Red-Eyes Alternative Black Dragon!

V0304_13_00_35_0.text:
C'mon out!
Meteor Black Comet Dragon!

V0304_13_00_36_0.text: Here comes Archfiend Black Skull Dragon!

V0304_15_00_00_0.text: I'm not da type to back down!

V0304_19_00_30_0.text: The Black Stone of Legend attacks!

V0304_19_00_33_0.text:
Red-Eyes Black Flare Dragon!
Take 'em out!

V0304_19_00_34_0.text:
Red-Eyes Alternative Black Dragon!
Burn 'em up!

V0304_19_00_37_0.text:
Meteor Black Comet Dragon!
Blow 'em away!

V0304_19_00_38_0.text: Archfiend Black Skull Dragon will send you packin'!

V0304_28_00_00_0.text: I'm gonna be a pro Duelist someday!

V0304_28_00_00_1.text:
So I can't lose today!
Or tomorrow!
Or tomorrow's tomorrow!

V0304_28_00_01_1.text: Dat's what separates the champs from the chumps!

V0304_28_00_02_0.text: I'm gettin' closer to becomin' a true Duelist!

V0304_28_00_03_1.text: Not if I'm gonna be as great as my buddy!

V0304_28_00_04_0.text: Looks like you're da one who needs to step up his game!

V0304_28_00_05_0.text:
I knew it!
You're still the same ol' kid!

V0304_28_00_06_0.text:
Oh yeah!
I'm on my A game!

V0304_28_00_06_1.text:
In Dueling, that is.
Not in class.

V0304_28_00_07_1.text:
So buy me the new Duel Disk!
Like ya promised!

V0304_28_00_08_0.text:
Teleport on home!
It's past your bedtime!

V0304_28_00_10_1.text: My Dueling is more powerful than my fists!

V0304_29_00_00_0.text:
Dis doesn't mean I'm givin' up!
I'll win next time!

V0304_29_00_02_0.text:
I lost.
You sure got skills.

V0304_29_00_03_0.text:
Ya serious?
Where did I go wrong?

V0304_29_00_04_0.text:
Argh!
I'll get ya someday, Kaiba!

V0304_29_00_04_1.text:
And when I do, I'm throwin' a party!
And you ain't invited!

V0304_29_00_05_0.text:
Are you really Mokuba?
Cuz the Mokuba I know ain't dis good!

V0304_29_00_06_1.text: Maybe turnin' pro is gonna be a dream forever...

V0304_29_00_07_0.text:
I lost... to Tristan...
I'll never be a pro...

V0304_29_00_08_0.text:
Aigami...
Who - or what - are you?

V0304_29_00_10_0.text:
Argh...
You better not do nuthin' bad, Scud...

V0304_29_00_11_0.text:
Well, dis wasn't a shocker.
You're tough as always.

V0304_33_00_02_0.text: I got a lil' ace up my sleeve!

V0304_34_00_00_0.text: I gotta believe to get thru this...

V0304_34_00_02_0.text: Dis deck is as important as my life!

V0304_34_00_03_0.text: I'm worthy of da new Duel Disk!

V0304_34_00_07_0.text: Argh! Even amateurs wouldn't make dat mistake!

V0304_34_00_09_0.text: I figured out your weak points!

V0304_35_00_01_0.text: First, I'm gonna win da Regionals!

V0304_36_00_00_0.text: You can mop 'em up for me!

V0304_36_00_01_0.text:
It's your turn.
Stay on guard!

V0304_36_00_02_0.text:
Sorry...
But I know you got dis!

V0304_36_00_04_0.text:
Okay!
I'm passin' the baton to you!

V0304_36_00_05_0.text: Sorry I put ya in dis mess, Yugi.

V0304_36_00_07_0.text: Don't make any dumb mistakes, Tristan!
